《'''華爾街之狼'''》（{{lang-en|'''''The Wolf of Wall Street'''''}}）是一本由前股票經紀人和商人[[喬丹·貝爾福特|喬丹·貝爾福特]]所寫的非小說回憶錄，2007年9月25日由{{link-en|矮腳雞圖書出版公司|Bantam Books}}負責出版。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.amazon.com/Wolf-Wall-Street-Jordan-Belfort/dp/0553805460/ref=tmm_hrd_swatch_0?_encoding=UTF8&sr=&qid= |title = The Wolf of Wall Street by Jordan Belfort |publisher = amazon.com |language = en |access-date = 2016-11-13 |archive-date = 2021-03-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210304231439/https://www.amazon.com/Wolf-Wall-Street-Jordan-Belfort/dp/0553805460/ref=tmm_hrd_swatch_0?_encoding=UTF8&sr=&qid= |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.goodreads.com/book/show/522776.The_Wolf_of_Wall_Street |title = The Wolf of Wall Street (The Wolf Of Wall Street #1) by Jordan Belfort (Goodreads Author) |publisher = Goodreads |language = en |access-date = 2016-11-13 |archive-date = 2018-07-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180725214617/https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/522776.The_Wolf_of_Wall_Street |dead-url = no }}</ref>這是他的第一本著作，下一本為《{{link-en|抓住華爾街之狼|Catching the Wolf of Wall Street}}》，於2009年出版。

此書於2013年改編成[[華爾街狼人|同名電影]]，由[[馬丁·史柯西斯|馬丁·史柯西斯]]執導，[[李奧納多·狄卡皮歐|李奧納多·狄卡皮歐]]飾演貝爾福特。

== 概要 ==
在書中，喬丹·貝爾福特講述他自己創立{{link-en|史崔頓證券公司|Stratton Oakmont}}的真實故事。該公司於1990年代晚期被監管機構倒閉，貝爾福特也因證券詐騙而入獄。

